summary:
Digital entrepreneur with four own start-ups and two executive positions in scale-ups. Most recent start-up, Playable Platform, was acquired by Huuuge Games, a major international mobile games company. 

Previously Consultant with BCG in New York. M.B.A. from MIT Sloan School of Management. M.Sc. in Financial Mathematics and Computer Science.
